      <title>数十名劳工立法者呼吁斯塔默辞职，斯塔默面临的压力越来越大</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/world/europe/starmer-speech-uk-labour.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，随着几名政府助手宣布辞职，总理基尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）面临领导挑战的可能性似乎急剧上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/world/europe/starmer-speech-uk-labour.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 21:41:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
