    <item>
      <title>为什么共和党仍在绘制众议院地图，而民主党则陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/politics/redistricting-republicans-democrats.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党得益于两项法院裁决，该党在选区重新划分方面占据了优势，并且在中期选举前有更多的回旋空间来争取额外席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/politics/redistricting-republicans-democrats.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 20:36:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>弗吉尼亚州官员要求最高法院恢复民主党绘制的投票地图</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/politics/supreme-court-virginia-redistricting.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州官员要求法官推翻弗吉尼亚州最高法院的一项裁决，该裁决推翻了国会地图，这是民主党的重大失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/politics/supreme-court-virginia-redistricting.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 20:03:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院在几天内继续通过邮寄方式获取堕胎药</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/politics/supreme-court-abortion-pill-mifepristone.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法官塞缪尔·A·阿利托 (Samuel A. Alito Jr.) 至少在周四暂停了联邦上诉法院对美国食品和药物管理局限制邮寄米非司酮的裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/politics/supreme-court-abortion-pill-mifepristone.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 20:03:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小罗伯特·肯尼迪正在推动对疫苗的大规模调查，尽管他在公开场合保持沉默</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/health/kennedy-vaccine-safety.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据白宫的命令，卫生部长小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪缓和了对疫苗的公开批评。但在他的部门内部，广泛的研究工作是首要任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/health/kennedy-vaccine-safety.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 20:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投票权决定可能会让田纳西州费耶特县的黑人保持沉默</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/fayette-county-tennessee-voting-rights.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[占田纳西州费耶特县 25% 的黑人居民去年赢得了新的选举地图，从而改变了全白人委员会。他们担心最高法院的裁决可能会威胁到这一点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/fayette-county-tennessee-voting-rights.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 19:49:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
